 p.m. to 8:00 p.m. at the City Center at Hanna Avenue (2555 East Hanna Aven
 ue). Members of the public can attend in-person at City Center at Hanna Av
 enue or virtually participate in this public meeting by using what is refe
 rred to by Florida Statutes and Council rules as communications media tech
