DESCRIPTION:The Ybor City Saturday Market is open every Saturday at Centen
 nial Park. Meet and shop from local artists and pick up some locally made 
 gourmet treats and produce. For additional information\, please visit the 
 Ybor Market. (https:ybormarket.com) \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/n
