 ch 10\, 2026 Time: 6:00pm to 9:00pm Location: Old City Hall  Sister Cities
  Room 315 East Kennedy Boulevard Tampa\, Florida 33602 Facilitator Robert 
 Hendrickson will facilitate meetings of the 2025 Charter Review Advisory C
 ommission. The commissions purpose is to review the Tampa Home Rule Charte
 r of 1975\, as amended\, and propose any amendments or revisions by majori
 ty vote of the Commission\, and present a report with their recommendation
 s to City Council\, which may by two-thirds vote of City Council be placed
