 tes
DESCRIPTION:Floridians have been hit hard by skyrocketing electricity bill
 s\, but our elected officials can do something about it! Join the Hillsbor
 ough Affordable Energy Coalition (HAEC) for a community discussion about r
 ising energy bills and how we can address this widely and deeply felt prob
 lem. Youll have the opportunity to share your personal story\, speak with 
