 d. Beginners start with a hand-building project to get acquainted with the
  clay and then jump into learning how to create their next ceramic adventu
 re. Intermediate students can dive right into getting dirty and take inspi
 ration from instructor-led projects. All experience levels are welcome! 18
  Classes Available  Jan 15-Mar 5 (7 classes)\, Mar 12-April 30 (7 classes 
 No class Mar 19 Firing costs\, essential tools\, and glazes included. Clay
  is available for purchase separately in studio. \n\nPermalink: https://ww
 w.tampa.gov/node/177131
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/177131
END:VEVENT
