SUMMARY:St Patrick039\\\;s Day Bottomless Brunch
LOCATION:401 E Jackson St. Suite 101 Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Join us at Top Shelf Sports Lounge Downtown for our St. Patric
 ks Day Brunch Party from 11AM2PM \, where the mimosas are bottomless\, the
  beer is green\, and the brunch buffet is fully loaded. Were serving up an
  All-You-Can-Eat Brunch Buffet packed with all your favorites to fuel a fu
 ll day of celebrating\, plus Bottomless Mimosas and Bottomless Green Beer 
 flowing all brunch long. If thats not enough\, well also have additional S
 t. Patricks Day drink specials to keep the party going. Live music will be
  playing throughout brunch to set the vibe\, so grab your friends\, wear s
 omething green\, and settle in for a festive afternoon of food\, drinks\, 
 and music in the heart of Downtown. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/n
