 ed services are invited to attend this Bridges to Business event focused o
 n Job Order Contracting (JOC) opportunities with the City of Tampa. Meet C
 ity-contracted prime firms and explore upcoming small- to medium-sized com
 mercial construction jobs and residential rehabilitation projects . Attend
 ees will also have the opportunity to: Connect directly with prime contrac
 tors currently working with the City Register for bid notifications Learn 
