SUMMARY:CREW Tampa Bay Pearls of Influence Breakfast
LOCATION:211 North Tampa Street Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Come celebrate CREW Tampa Bays 30th Anniversary event featurin
 g national speaker\, renowned investment banker and published author Carla
  Harris\, vice chairman and managing director at Morgan Stanley and former
  chair of the National Womens Business Council. Carla will share her eight
  pearls of intentional leadership: authenticity\, building trust\, creatin
 g other leaders\, clarity\, diversity\, innovation\, inclusivity and voice
 . Carla was most recently a Vice Chairman responsible for increasing clien
 t connectivity and penetration to enhance revenue generation across the fi
 rm. She was the founder and creator of the award winning\, Multicultural I
 nnovation Lab at Morgan Stanley\, and the award-winning podcast\, Access a
 nd Opportunity. In her 30 year career\, Carla has had extensive industry e
 xperiences in the technology\, media\, retail\, telecommunications\, trans
 portation\, industrial\, and healthcare sectors. In August 2013\, Carla wa
 s appointed by President Barack Obama to chair the National Womens Busines
 s Council. Dont miss this amazing opportunity to showcase your business in
  front of hundreds of movers and shakers in the commercial real estate ind
 ustry! Sponsoring the CREW Tampa Bay 30 Year Anniversary Celebration offer
 s unparalleled exposure to key local CRE professionals and potential clien
 ts\, enhancing your brands visibility. Additionally\, your support will di
 rectly contribute to scholarships and leadership programs\, aligning your 
 company with a meaningful cause while fostering valuable business connecti
 ons. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/186491
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/186491
END:VEVENT
