SUMMARY:Water Days
LOCATION:4801 E Fowler Ave. Tampa \, FL 33617 United States
DESCRIPTION:Start by exploring a variety of interactive learning stations 
 led by MOSI educators\, community partners\, and local experts. Hands-on l
 earning makes stormwater science\, conservation practices\, and sustainabi
 lity easy to understand for all ages. Next\, take a closer look at real ch
 allenges facing Tampa Bay. Water Days highlights stormwater issues and lon
 g-term environmental resilience. The event also centers on communities mos
 t affected by these challenges. This event is included with general admiss
 ion and FREE for MOSI Members . Throughout the day\, families can enjoy en
 vironmental science activities and receive sustainability-themed giveaways
  while supplies last. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/186511
