 ttps:www.marriott.comen-ushotelstpajd-jw-marriott-tampa-water-streetovervi
 ew)\, Driftlight Steakhouse (https:www.driftlighttampa.com) offers an eleg
 ant yet inviting atmosphere where regional\, farm-and ocean-to-table cuisi
 ne takes center stage. Join us on April 28th for an unforgettable evening 
 at our Silver Oak Wine Dinner. Savor a meticulously crafted multi course m
 enu\, expertly paired with distinguished Silver Oak vintages for a truly e
 xquisite culinary journey. Elevate your night with exceptional flavors\, i
 mpeccable service\, and an ambiance designed for discerning tastes. Seats 
 are limited\, with pricing starting at 295 per person. Reserve your place 
 today online (https:www.opentable.combookingexperiences-availability?rid11
 41729 restref1141729 experienceId671786 utm_sourceexternal utm_mediumrefer
 ral utm_campaignshared)or by calling (813) 314-6611. Make it a staycation 
 with the Savor Spring on Water Street package (https:www.marriott.comoffer
 ssavor-spring-on-water-street-off-214817tpajd-jw-marriott-tampa-water-stre
 et)\, which includes a 100 hotel credit and an upgraded water view. \n\nPe
 rmalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/187421
